CustomField.FSL__Service_Goal__c.FSL__Use_Exact_Location.HelpText	Make sure that the mobile worker first completes all jobs at one location with identical latitude and longitude, before moving on to the next location at the same site. For example, use if you have multiple jobs within close proximity without connecting roads between them, such as a campus, or farm.
