Flow.AutoLaunchedFlow.FSL__Send_Email_For_Automated_Bundling_Failures.10.TextTemplate.EmailBodyTextTemplate.FieldLabel	<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Salesforce Sans&quot;, sans-serif;">Hello {!userName},</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Salesforce Sans&quot;, sans-serif;">We wanted to inform you that {!countAutomatedBundlingOptimizationRequests} of your optimization requests failed.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Salesforce Sans&quot;, sans-serif;">Type: Automated Bundling</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Salesforce Sans&quot;, sans-serif;">To learn more about the failed request, see </span><a href="https://help.salesforce.com/s/articleView?id=sf.pfs_monitor_optimization_requests.htm&amp;type=5" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" 
Flow.AutoLaunchedFlow.FSL__Send_Email_For_Automated_Bundling_Failures.10.TextTemplate.EmailSubjectTextTemplate.FieldLabel	Salesforce Field Service Automated Bundling schedule optimization request failed
